Owners.com, Inc.


                  Owners.com, Inc., a subsidiary of Altisource Portfolio Solutions SA, is an American company located in San Francisco, CA, that operates an Internet-based residential real estate brokerage business. Altisource Portfolio Solutions SA acquired Owners.com, Inc. on 24 Nov 14 for $27 million.                




